title: Ep 247 - Diwali With Gokuldham
shortDesc: The members of Gokuldham are very excited to celebrate Diwali, the festival of lights. Watch this episode to see how Gokuldham society members celebrate Diwali.

title: Ep 248 - Jethalal Gets A Mobile For Babita
shortDesc: Babita is looking for a new phone to gift her brother. She approaches Jetha for the phone. Will Jetha be able to get the phone or not? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 249 - Sundar Takes The Red Cherry Phone Away
shortDesc: Champaklal, while trying to look for his spectacles packs the phone in Sundar's bag. How will Iyer receive the new Red Cherry Phone?

title: Ep 250 - Jetha In Trouble
shortDesc: Jethalal tries to contact Sundar with Taarak's help. Meanwhile, Iyer asks Jethalal about the phone which leads Jethalal to explode. Watch this episode to find out what happens next.

title: Ep 252 - Jethalal And Daya At War
shortDesc: Sundar returns from Bangalore but forgets his bags in the taxi. Meanwhile, Daya and Jetha continue to fight. Will they make up for themselves? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 253 - Daya Leaves Jethalal
shortDesc: After falsely accusing Daya's brother, Jethalal feels guilty about it. But, Daya decides to keep her word and leaves Jethalal with her brother. Will she come back? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 254 - Jethalal Seeks For Taaraks Help
tags: jetha seeks for taaraks help   taarak comes up with a backup plan to help his friend out before babita asks again
not being sure whether sundar has the mobile phone or not
shortDesc: Not being sure whether Sundar has the mobile phone or not, Jetha seeks for Taarak's help.  Taarak comes up with a backup plan to help his friend out before Babita asks again.

title: Ep 255 - Too Many Mobile Phones
shortDesc: To save their relationships with one another, Sundar and Jethalal buy a new red cherry mobile each and hide them. Will they get into a bigger mess? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 256 - Champaklal Solves The Problem
shortDesc: Jethalal finds the phone in Sundar's bag. Daya decides to leave the house but, Champaklal steps in and solves the chaos. Watch this episode to find out how.

title: Ep 257 - Tappu Wins A Prize At The Camp
shortDesc: The kids return from the camp and narrate their stories to Champaklal. Later, Tappu says that he won the 'Best Boy' prize in the camp. Watch this episode to know how the kids had fun in the camp.

title: Ep 258 - Taaraks Mind Block.
shortDesc: Taarak Mehta is having a mind block and is finding new ways to write a new article. Later, Tappu creates a problem to drink milk while Jetha is on a business call. Will Jetha scold him? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 259 - Tappu Senas TV Ad.
shortDesc: Rita visits Gokuldham Society and asks the parents if Tappu Sena can audition for a TV advertisement. How will the parents react? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 260 - Audition Day.
shortDesc: Tappu Sena is excited about their auditions but, their parents are more excited about their auditions. Will the kids get through the auditions? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 261 - Daya Admires Sodhi.
shortDesc: After the auditions, the members of Gokuldham society return home. Daya observes Sodhi's excitement about the audition and love for his son and admires his fatherhood.

title: Ep 262 - Roshan Singh Sodhi Is Disappointed
shortDesc: Roshan Sodhi learns that all the kids have got selected for the ad shoot except for Gogi. He makes a scene for this issue and makes sure everyone knows that he is disappointed. Later, the rest of the kids go to the shoot and become famous.
